quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  67,15,"Shi, (Allah), Yã sanya muku ƙasa hõrarriya, sai ku tafi cikin sãsanninta, kuma ku ci daga arzikin Sa, kuma zuwa gare shi ne tãshin yake"
  67,16,"Shin kõ kun amince cewa wanda ke cikin sama, bã zai iya shãfe ƙasa tãre da ku ba, sai ga ta tana mai girgiza"
  67,17,"Kõ kun amincẽ cewa wanda ke cikin sama bã zai iya sako muku iskar gũguwa ba? To, zã ku san yadda (ãƙibar) gargaɗi Na take"
  67,18,"Lalle, waɗanda ke gabansu sun ƙaryata (manzanni). To, yãya (ãƙibar) gargaɗi Na ta kasance"
  67,19,"Bã zã su yi dũbi ba zuwa ga tsuntsãye a kansu, mãsu sanwã, kuma suna fiffikãwa, bãbu mai riƙe da su sai (Allah), Mairahama? Lalle shi Mai gani ne ga dukan kõme"
  67,20,"Wãne ne wanda zai zame muku mayãƙin da zai taimake ku, wanda bã (Allah) ba, Mai rahama? Kãfirai ba su a cikin kõme fãce rũɗu"
  67,21,"Wãne ne wanda zai ciyar da ku, idan (Allah) Ya riƙe arzikin Sa? A'aha, sun yi zurfi cikin girman kai da tãshin hankali"
  67,22,"Shin, wanda ke tafiya a kife a kan fuskarsa yã fi zama a kan shiryuwa, ko kuwa wanda ke tafiya miƙe a kan hanya madaidaiciya"
  67,23,"Ka ce: \"(Allah) Shine Wanda Ya ƙaga halittarku, Ya sanya muku ji da gani da tunãni, amman kaɗan ce ƙwarai godiyarku"
  67,24,"Kuma kace \"Shi ne Ya halitta ku daga ƙasã, kuma zuwa gare Shi ne ake tãshin ku"
  67,25,"Kuma sunã cewa, \"Yaushe ne wannan alkawarin zai tabbata in dai kun kasance mãsu gaskiya ne kũ"
  67,26,"Ka ce: \"Ilmin a wurin Allah kawai yake, kuma ni mai gargaɗi kawai ne, mai bayyana (gargaɗin)"
  67,27,"To, lokacin da suka gan ta (azãbar) a kusa, fuskokin waɗanda suka kãfirta suka mũnana, kuma aka ce (musu) wannan shi ne abin da kuka zamo kuna ƙaryatãwa"
  67,28,"Ka ce musu \"Idan Allah Ya halaka ni nĩ da wanda ke tãre da ni, ko kuma, Yã yi mana rahama, to, wãne ne zai tserar da kafirai daga wata azãba mai raɗaɗi"
  67,29,"Ka ce: \"Shĩ ne Mai rahama mun yi ĩmãni da Shi, gare Shi muka dogara, saboda haka zã ku san wanda yake a cikin ɓata bayyananniya"
  67,30,"Ka ce: \"Ko kun gani, idan ruwanku ya wãyi gari faƙaƙƙe, to, wãne ne zai zo muku da ruwa wani mai ɓuɓɓuga"